Game : Spiderman
Date : 2004/11/05 
Video: PAL
Ripped by: DCP
Rip notes: Down Sampled The FMV's 

Get out your red & blue suit and swing through this action/adventure game for all Spiderman fans brought too you by the team behind Tony Hawks Pro Skater. 
 
Featuring all your favourite Spiderman bad guys like Venom and Rhino, battle your way through the comic book inspired story and save New York from certain  destruction.
 
 New York & the world need a hero .. that hero is you